{"time": "2026-05-25T19:10:22", "level": "DEBUG", "name": "openai._base_client", "message": "Request options: {'method': 'post', 'url': '/chat/completions', 'files': None, 'idempotency_key': 'stainless-python-retry-3cf0e82b-c8c9-48bb-bf15-dba0b8313729', 'security': {'bearer_auth': True}, 'content': None, 'json_data': {'messages': [{'role': 'system', 'content': '你是一个风控特征质量评审专家。'}, {'role': 'user', 'content': '你是一个风控特征质量评审专家。请分析低效特征并给出具体修正建议。\n\n## 评审维度\n- time_window: 时间窗口不合适\n- filter_condition: 过滤条件可优化\n- aggregation: 聚合函数选择不当\n- transformation: 变换方式需调整\n- direction_shift: 建议切换到其他方向\n\n## 业务先验模板\n- 交易类特征: 时效性高，推荐 1d-7d 窗口，关注金额分布和频次\n- 设备类特征: 稳定性重要，推荐 7d-30d 窗口，关注设备切换和异常标记\n- 地理类特征: 稀疏性高，推荐较长窗口，关注跳跃距离和跨境行为\n- 行为类特征: 周期性明显，推荐 7d-14d 窗口，关注时序模式\n- 网络类特征: 图结构重要，推荐聚合邻居属性\n\n## 低效特征列表\n{"feature_id": "FEAT_USER_DEVICE_RISK_ROOT_COUNT_7D_001", "direction": "user_device_risk", "definition": {"source_table": "user_device_log", "time_window": "7d", "filter": "root_status=1", "aggregation": "COUNT", "transformation": "RAW"}, "IV": 0.0, "KS": 0.0, "missing_rate": 0.0, "status": "skipped", "reason": "insufficient bins after filtering"}\n{"feature_id": "FEAT_USER_DEVICE_RISK_EMULATOR_COUNT_30D_001", "direction": "user_device_risk", "definition": {"source_table": "device_fingerprint", "time_window": "30d", "filter": "emulator_flag=1", "aggregation": "COUNT", "transformation": "RAW"}, "IV": 4e-05, "KS": 0.0029, "missing_rate": 0.0, "status": "skipped", "reason": "IV=0.000040 < 0.005"}\n{"feature_id": "FEAT_USER_DEVICE_RISK_ACTIVE_DEVICES_1D_001", "direction": "user_device_risk", "definition": {"source_table": "user_device_log", "time_window": "1d", "filter": "1=1", "aggregation": "COUNT_DISTINCT", "transformation": "RAW"}, "IV": 0.0, "KS": 0.0, "missing_rate": 0.0, "status": "skipped", "reason": "insufficient bins after filtering"}\n\n请为每个低效特征给出修正建议，返回 JSON 格式：{"critiques": [...]}'}], 'model': 'deepseek-v4-flash', 'max_tokens': 1024, 'response_format': {'type': 'json_object'}, 'temperature': 0.3}}"}
