{"time": "2026-05-25T19:13:35", "level": "DEBUG", "name": "openai._base_client", "message": "Request options: {'method': 'post', 'url': '/chat/completions', 'files': None, 'idempotency_key': 'stainless-python-retry-d517a757-da7a-4148-8205-99272799b163', 'security': {'bearer_auth': True}, 'content': None, 'json_data': {'messages': [{'role': 'system', 'content': '你是一个专业的风控特征挖掘系统。'}, {'role': 'user', 'content': '你是一个风控特征挖掘专家。你需要生成风险特征定义(FeatureDSL)。\n\n## 规则\n1. 每个特征的 feature_id 格式为 FEAT_{DIRECTION}_{READABLE_MEANING}_{WINDOW}_{INDEX}，必须使用英文大写、数字和下划线，名称要能看出业务含义\n2. time_window 格式为 数字+单位，如 7d, 24h, 30m\n3. filter 必须是合法 SQL WHERE 子句，不得包含未来数据（如 t+1, tomorrow）\n4. aggregation 必须是以下之一: COUNT, SUM, AVG, MAX, MIN, STDDEV, COUNT_DISTINCT, RATIO, FREQUENCY\n5. transformation 必须是以下之一: RAW, LOG, WOE, BIN, STANDARDIZE, MINMAX, QUANTILE_BIN\n6. compliance_tags 必须包含 PII_FREE 和 EXPLAINABLE\n7. 不得使用敏感字段: id_number, phone, name, email_raw\n8. 每个特征必须有不同的业务含义\n\n## DSL Schema\n{\n  "$schema": "http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#",\n  "title": "FeatureDSL",\n  "description": "特征挖掘 DSL Schema，约束生成器输出的特征定义结构",\n  "type": "object",\n  "required": ["feature_id", "direction", "definition", "business_logic", "compliance_tags"],\n  "properties": {\n    "feature_id": {\n      "type": "string",\n      "pattern": "^FEAT_[A-Z0-9_]+$",\n      "description": "唯一特征标识符"\n    },\n    "direction": {\n      "type": "string",\n      "enum": [\n        "user_device_risk",\n        "transaction_pattern",\n        "geolocation_anomaly",\n        "account_behavior",\n        "network_relation"\n      ],\n      "description": "特征挖掘方向"\n    },\n    "definition": {\n      "type": "object",\n      "required": ["source_table", "time_window", "filter", "aggregation", "transformation"],\n      "properties": {\n        "source_table": {\n          "type": "string",\n          "description": "数据源表名"\n        },\n        "time_window": {\n          "type": "string",\n          "pattern": "^\\\\d+[dhm]$",\n          "description": "时间窗口，如 7d, 24h, 30m"\n        },\n        "filter": {\n          "type": "string",\n          "description": "过滤条件，SQL WHERE 子句风格"\n        },\n        "aggregation": {\n          "type": "string",\n          "enum": ["COUNT", "SUM", "AVG", "MAX", "MIN", "STDDEV", "COUNT_DISTINCT", "RATIO", "FREQUENCY"],\n          "description": "聚合函数"\n        },\n        "transformation": {\n          "type": "string",\n          "enum": ["RAW", "LOG", "WOE", "BIN", "STANDARDIZE", "MINMAX", "QUANTILE_BIN"],\n          "description": "变换方法"\n        }\n      }\n    },\n    "business_logic": {\n      "type": "string",\n      "minLength": 1,\n      "description": "业务含义说明"\n    },\n    "compliance_tags": {\n      "type": "array",\n      "items": {"type": "string"},\n      "minItems": 1,\n      "description": "合规标签列表"\n    }\n  }\n}\n\n## 当前搜索方向\nCURRENT_DIRECTION: account_behavior\n聚焦账户行为模式，如表: account_login_log, user_profile。常用字段: login_time, login_ip, register_days, kyc_level\n\n## 当前生成策略\n- TEMPLATE_FAMILY: anomaly_distance\n- TRANSFORM_STRATEGY: missing_indicator\n构造偏离常态、距离、异常程度特征。\n显式利用缺失模式或补充缺失指示。\n\n## 历史优秀因子\n暂无可复用优秀因子。\n\n## 历史反馈\n- [FEAT_TRANSACTION_PATTERN_CHANNEL_RATIO_7D_001] IV=0.000000, KS=0.0000, 区分度不足 | 修正轴: transformation | 建议: 建议使用 WOE 或 LOG 变换提高区分度\n- [FEAT_TRANSACTION_PATTERN_AMOUNT_SHARE_1D_003] IV=0.000000, KS=0.0000, 区分度不足 | 修正轴: filter_condition | 建议: 建议增加有效样本过滤条件\n- [FEAT_GEO_CITY_CHANGES_1D_001] IV=0.000000, KS=0.0000, 区分度不足 | 修正轴: time_window | 建议: 建议缩短时间窗口以提高时效性\n\n## 防泄漏规则\n- 时间窗口不超过 365 天\n- 禁止使用 t+1, tomorrow, future 等未来数据关键词\n- 禁止在 filter 中使用标签字段（如 label, target）\n\n请生成 3 个特征定义，以 JSON 格式返回：{"features": [...]}'}], 'model': 'deepseek-v4-flash', 'max_tokens': 2048, 'response_format': {'type': 'json_object'}, 'temperature': 0.7}}"}
